#

Shrimp Scampi with Garlic Bread

$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

SeafoodHigh ProteinQuick Meal

Tags:

EasyGourmetComfort Food

Description

Succulent shrimp sautéed in a garlic butter sauce, served with crispy garlic bread for dipping.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • Garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Parsley (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • Red pepper flakes: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • French bread (for garlic bread): 1 loaf
  • Parmesan cheese (grated): 1/4 cup
